               <msContents>
                  <summary>Acts of Krestos Samra, ገድለ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሠምራ፡, Miracles of Krestos Samra, ተአምረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሰምራ፡, Image of Krestos Samra, መልክአ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሠምራ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="67v" facs="005"/><title>Acts of Krǝstos Śämra, Gädlä Kǝrǝstos Śämra, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገድለ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሠምራ፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንጽሕፍ፡ ዝክረ፡ ውዳሴሃ፡ ለእምነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሠምራ፡ ዘወሐባ፡ ኪዳነ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ሰማይ፡ ወምድር፡ ወሀለወት፡ አሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ እምአህጉረ፡ ሸዋ፡ ሀገረ፡ ሙላዳ፡ ለእምነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሠምራ፡ ሀገረ፡ ቡልጋ፡ ቅዱስጌ፡ ቅድስት፡ ወነበሩ፡ አቡሃ፡ ወእማ፡ ኄራነ፡ ወፈራህያነ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወወላዱ፡ ወለተ፡ ኅሪተ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>in Gǝ‘ǝz and Amharic</note>
                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                    <locus target="#67v" facs="072"/>
                    “This book was written in the reign of King Ḫaylä Śǝllase (2 April 1930–12 September 1974).” The scribe’s name is: Gäbrä Ḥǝywät
                  </colophon>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="68r" to="74r" facs="072"/><title>Three Miracles of Krǝstos Śämra, Tä’amǝrä Kǝrǝstos Śämra, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተአምረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሠምራ፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1"><locus from="68r" to="70v" facs="072"/><title>First Miracle: On the death of Krǝstos Śämra: How a certain monk named Isaac found the body of our mother, Krǝstos Śämra; how he vowed to stay there with her body until he died, and how he died after forty days</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2"><locus from="70v" to="72v" facs="075"/><title>Second Miracle: How Krǝstos Śämra spoke to Filipos when she died</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3"><locus from="72v" to="74r" facs="077"/><title>Third Miracle: How the Virgin Mary appeared to our mother, Krǝstos Śämra</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
              </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="74v" to="89r" facs="079"/><title>Image of Krǝstos Śämra, Mälǝkǝ’a Kǝrǝstos Śämra, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክአ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሠምራ፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ ሥምረቱ፡
                    እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ካህን እንተ፡ አንበቦ፡ እምጥንቱ፡
                    ሥምረተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሠምራ፡ እስመ፡ ኢየሐጽጸኪ፡ ለለዕለቱ፡
                    ተረክበ፡ ፍካሬሁ፡ ለንባበ፡ ስምኪ፡ ዝንቱ፡
                    ለኩሉሰ፡ ተንብዮ፡ ፍካሬ፡ አልቦቱ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  </msItem>
